Децимация¶

$ y(n) = x(nR), $ $R$ -- ,

: $ y(n) = \sum_{k=0}^{N-1}x(nR-k)h(k) $ ,

CIC-фильтр¶

: $$ H(f)=\left(\frac{sin(\pi RMf)}{sin(\pi f)}\right)^{N},$$ $M$ -- , 1;

$N$ -- .

CIC-фильтр дециматор¶

In [198]:
def cic_decimator(x, r, n):
    """
     cic_decimator
    CIC- 

      :
    x --  
    r --  
    n --  
    """
    y = x
    # Integrator stages
    for i in range(n):
        y = np.cumsum(y)
    # Decimator
    y = y[::r]
    # COMB stages
    y = np.diff(y, n=n, prepend=np.zeros(n))
    return y

Интерполяция¶

$ y(n) = \begin{cases} x(n/R) , n = 0, N, 2N, ...\\ 0 , n \ne 0, N, 2N, ... \end{cases} $, $R$ -- ,

: $ y(n) = \sum_{k=0}^{N-1}x(nR-k)h(k) $ ,

CIC-фильтр интерполятор¶

In [79]:
def cic_interpolator(x, r, n):
    """
     cic_interpolator
    CIC- 

      :
    x --  
    r --  
    n --  
    """
    y = x
    # COMB stages
    y = np.diff(y, n=n, prepend=np.zeros(n), append=np.zeros(n))
    #y = np.diff(y, n=n)
    
    # Interpolator
    y = np.array([i if j == 0 else 0 for i in y for j in range(r)])

    # integrator
    for i in range(n):
        y = np.cumsum(y)

    y = y[r - 1:-n*r+r-1]
    return y
